<title>USA: Neiman Marcus April same-store sales down.</title>
<headline>Neiman Marcus April same-store sales down.</headline>
<dateline>CHESTNUT HILL, Mass. 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Four weeks ended   May 3, 1997	 April 27, 1996     % Chg.</p>
<p>Total Revs	$ 154.8 million	$ 152.8 million    + 1.3%</p>
<p>Comparable Revs $ 152.4 million	$ 152.8 million    - 0.3%</p>
<p>				 39 weeks ended</p>
<p>			 May 3, 1997	 April 27, 1996     % Chg.</p>
<p>Total Revs	$1,713.2 million    $1,589.4 million    + 7.8%</p>
<p>Comparable Revs $ 1,661.0 million   $1,589.4 million    + 4.5%</p>
<p>Note: Fiscal year ends August 2, 1997.</p>
<p>Full company name: Neiman Marcus Group Inc.</p>
<p>-- New York Newsdesk</p>
